===Pronunciation===
יהּ / yâhh / yaw

===Etymology===
Contracted for [[יהוה]] {{HH|3068}}, and meaning the same; 

===Proper noun===
'''יהּ'''

# [[Jah]], the sacred name: - Jah, the [[Lord]], most vehement. Cp. names in “-iah,” “-jah.”

